query:
SELECT bd.employeeId, bd.weeklyRevenue, bd.bonusAmount, e.name, wb.weekNumber, wb.month, wb.year 
FROM bonusDetails bd 
LEFT JOIN employees e ON bd.employeeId = e.id 
LEFT JOIN weeklyBonuses wb ON bd.weeklyBonusId = wb.id 
WHERE wb.branchId = 1 
ORDER BY wb.id DESC, bd.id;
